# Language

Remember following when writing text

- we have only English and French support
- When adding any text make sure you translate it in french and english & if you notice any existing plain english text please add translations to it.

# Coding rules to remember:

- Make sure to use single responsibility design pattern
  - Always create files and mini components that does one job
  - Likewise, functions that do one job
- Goal for readability
- Add comments with examples and avoid frilly languages
- Don't created .md files unless I tell you.

# Writing Copy

- Write as a professional copywriter, avoid frilly language and don't sound so salesy but still influence and get the user to get the service
- Use tips and tricks of Alex Hormozi while you can
